{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, rotor angle stability is another area where data driven ML based approaches are frequently applied.",
    "In Amjady and Majedi (2007), the power system is partitioned into subsets each including two or more synchronous machines using the data from each partition.",
    "ANN is trained and final decision is obtained through a voting mechanism.",
    "Proximity to pre-identified voltage templates are used as features to a SVM classifier in Rajapakse et al. (2010) to differentiate rotor angle stability/instability.",
    "In Gomez et al. (2011), direct voltages measurements are input to a SVM classifier to predict the transient stability status after a disturbance."
  ]
}